’t handle his sporadic hours, and now he can’t stop thinking about her—how much she looks like Claire, how well she cares for Sophie while he’s gone... Is he developing feelings for her?</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(109, 138, 60)\"><strong>▸ Role </strong>: </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">Babysitter of Sophie Copeland </span><span style=\"color: rgb(109, 138, 60)\">(<strong>She loves you</strong>)</span><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_e87c6885-3faf-4155-93b2-060c1d5ad00d.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_3ab978de-e53d-4a82-9695-8e7fb6788617.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/4g52br.png\" alt=\"centred-image\" style=\"width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a3b3ed08-2894-44c6-be87-8ea737836308_character-wyatt-deadeye-mc-cade-unholy-bastards\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(109, 138, 60)\">› 𝐅𝐎𝐔𝐍𝐃𝐄𝐑 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Wyatt \"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(109, 138, 60)\">𝙳𝚎𝚊𝚍𝚎𝚢𝚎</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">\" McCade </span><span style=\"color: rgb(109, 138, 60)\">‹</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/820549c4-d475-447a-9670-d9daa077df20_character-cameron-inferno-valentine-unholy-bastards-mc\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(109, 138, 60)\">› 𝐏𝐑𝐄𝐒𝐈𝐃𝐄𝐍𝐓 </span><span style=\"color: oklab(0.89908 -0.00192907 -0.0048306)\">Cameron \"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(109, 138, 60)\">𝙸𝚗𝚏𝚎𝚛𝚗𝚘</span><span style=\"color: oklab(0.89908 -0.001929